@* ===========================================================================
   File        : AppFooter.razor
   Namespace   : AbsenceApp.Client.Components.Layout
   Author      : Michael
   Version     : 1.0.0
   Created     : 2026-03-17
   Updated     : 2026-03-17
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : Persistent footer bar rendered at the bottom of the main
                 content column.  Displays a copyright notice with the
                 current year resolved at render time.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Notes       :
     - DateTime.Now.Year is evaluated on each render; no code-behind
       is required.
     - Included directly in MainLayout below the <main> element.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-17  Initial implementation.
   ===========================================================================
*@

@* =========================================================================
   Section: Footer bar — copyright notice
   ========================================================================= *@
<footer class="app-footer">
    <span>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year AbsenceApp &mdash; All rights reserved.</span>
</footer>
